settings.temperature-tip: Random sampling ratio. High temperature produces more randomness, low temperature produces more concentrated and deterministic text.

settings.presence-penalty-tip: (PresencePenalty) Controls the likelihood of new topics generated by the model. Increasing this value can increase the likelihood of talking about new topics.
settings.frequency-penalty-tip: (FrequencyPenalty) Controls the degree of word repetition generated by the model. Increasing this value can reduce the possibility of word repetition.
settings.repetition-penalty-tip: (RepetitionPenalty) Controls the degree of repetition generated by the model. Increasing this value can reduce repetition, but may cause the model to generate incoherent text (similar to FrequencyPenalty).

charge.group-pricing-tip:
Multiplier can be used to distinguish the billing price of different user groups, * * The base multiplier is 1 * *, that is, * * user price = model price * multiplier * *

Example: If the model charges 0.2 points and the user group ratio is 0.8, the actual charge is 0.2 x 0.8 = 0.16 points

- Purchase multiplier: when the user purchases credits, the deduction price multiplier
- Consumption multiplier: the deduction price multiplier when the user spends credits

cdn.warm-tip:
> If you are using a CDN service, you can warm up resources with this feature.
* * After each update, you can perform a resource refresh to ensure the stability of the resource and increase the loading speed. * *
CDN (Content Delivery Network) resources are preheated, and after preheating, the resources will be cached to the CDN node to speed up access.
With the warm-up function, you can cache popular resources to the CDN node before the peak of business, reducing the pressure on the source station and improving the user experience.
Tip: * * Warm-up execution will pull a lot of data from the CDN to the source station, please pay attention to the source station's broadband load. * *

tiplist.wxpusher:
- WeChat Push using [WxPusher] (https://wxpusher.zjiecode.com) service
- Register and create an app on the WxPusher website
- Get the AppToken for the app and populate the configuration
- TopicId is optional for mass mailing
- Scan app QR code to follow to receive push
tiplist.discord:
- Discord push based on webhook mechanism
- Select the target channel in the Discord server
- Go to Channel Settings > Integrations > Create Webhook
- Custom webhook name and avatar (optional)
- Copy the generated webhook URL population configuration
tiplist.telegram:
- Telegram push needs to create its own bot
- Search for @ BotFather in Telegram and start a conversation
- Send the/newbot command and follow the prompts to set the bot name and username
- Get the Bot Token and populate the configuration
- Join or privately chat with a bot in a target group
- Use @ userinfobot to get the Chat ID of the chat and fill it in
tiplist.feishu:
- Flybook push uses group custom bots
- Adding custom bots to the target flying book group
- Set bot name, avatar and description
- Select the group that will receive the message
- Copy the generated webhook URL population configuration
- Keywords can be set for added security (optional)
tiplist.email: - Email push is the default option and notifications will be pushed to your registered email address
